title: #92Noon! Twins Talker Tuesday!
description: Twins catcher Mitch Garver & bench coach Derek Shelton both join in the first hour! More Kimbrel/Keuchel bits, Lavelle reports on the Cleveland series, and The Athletic's Zack Meisel offers intel on the Indians to close the show!
